<question type="multichoice">
  <name><text>CSIR PYQ Unit IV Q10 — Separable extension in char 0</text></name>
  <questiontext format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[If \(\mathrm{char}(F)=0\), then every algebraic extension \(K/F\) is:]]></text>
  </questiontext>
  <generalfeedback format="html">
    <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Answer: Separable.</strong><br>In characteristic 0, every irreducible polynomial \(f\in F[x]\) has no repeated roots (since \(\gcd(f,f')=1\): the formal derivative \(f'\ne 0\) and \(\deg f'<\deg f\) so they share no common irreducible factor). Therefore every algebraic extension in char 0 is separable.</p>]]></text>
  </generalfeedback>
